Dialogue: 2,0:00:01.12,0:00:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}大家好！我是叶修,
Dialogue: 2,0:00:04.02,0:00:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你们可以叫我叶老师！
Dialogue: 2,0:00:06.85,0:00:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}欢迎来到我英文课程。
Dialogue: 2,0:00:09.52,0:00:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们会在这堂课说英文。
Dialogue: 2,0:00:13.00,0:00:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}英文是我的母语，
Dialogue: 2,0:00:15.07,0:00:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以无论你在英文学习的哪个阶段，我都可以教！
Dialogue: 2,0:00:21.20,0:00:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那如果你以前从未学过英文,
Dialogue: 2,0:00:25.42,0:00:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而且不明白我在说什么，没事，
Dialogue: 2,0:00:28.65,0:00:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我可以和你说中文。
Dialogue: 2,0:00:30.70,0:00:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是我才学中文一年，
Dialogue: 2,0:00:33.30,0:00:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以希望我们之间尽量说英文!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:38.47,0:00:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我觉得学习语言的最好方法是学习一个国家的文化，
Dialogue: 2,0:00:45.37,0:00:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以，在我的课上，你可以了解到北美文化。
Dialogue: 2,0:00:51.55,0:00:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你已经有一本英文书,
Dialogue: 2,0:00:55.07,0:00:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我可以帮助你解决书上的问题!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:59.40,0:01:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那接下来，让我们一起学英文吧!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.65,0:01:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And if you're not a Chinese speaker, that's totally fine.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.87,0:01:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}My name is Brad, and I come from Vancouver, Canada.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.77,0:01:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)\fscx93\fscy93}And as someone who's already learning a second language, I understand how hard it can be.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.95,0:01:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}To understand people when they talk too fast
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.73,0:01:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}or understand how to read efficiently
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.81,0:01:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}or understand how to speak with decent pronunciation.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.45,0:01:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But in my class, I want to go at the speed of the student.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.52,0:01:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And so if you feel that you're not understanding a study question or a certain topic,
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.03,0:01:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}we won't move on until you do.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.50,0:01:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And I want to be available to my students.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.00,0:01:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And so once we're in class, I'll be happy to give you my WhatsApp.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.40,0:01:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And anytime you have questions about homework or anything English related,
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.36,0:01:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}feel free to message me, and I'll get right back to you.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.17,0:01:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm more than excited to help you on your English journey, and I'll see you in class.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:03.65,0:01:06.87,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你不会说中文，那也没关系。
Dialogue: 2,0:01:06.87,0:01:09.77,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我叫Brad，来自加拿大温哥华。
Dialogue: 2,0:01:09.77,0:01:14.95,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}作为一个已经在学习第二语言的人，我能理解其中的困难。
Dialogue: 2,0:01:14.95,0:01:17.73,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当人们说话太快时如何理解，
Dialogue: 2,0:01:17.73,0:01:20.81,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}或者如何高效阅读，
Dialogue: 2,0:01:20.81,0:01:25.45,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}或者如何做到优秀的发音。
Dialogue: 2,0:01:25.45,0:01:28.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是在我的课堂上，我想以学生可接受的速度进行。
Dialogue: 2,0:01:28.52,0:01:34.03,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以如果你觉得不理解某个问题或某个主题，
Dialogue: 2,0:01:34.03,0:01:36.50,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们会直到你理解再继续。
Dialogue: 2,0:01:36.50,0:01:39.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我希望更好地服务学生，
Dialogue: 2,0:01:39.00,0:01:42.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以上课时，我会告诉你们我的WhatsApp。
Dialogue: 2,0:01:42.40,0:01:47.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你有任何关于作业或任何英语相关的问题，
Dialogue: 2,0:01:47.36,0:01:50.17,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}请随时给我发信息 ，我会尽快回复。
Dialogue: 2,0:01:50.17,0:01:54.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我非常高兴能在你的英语之旅中帮助你，我们课上见！
Dialogue: 1,0:00:01.12,0:00:04.02,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hello everyone! My name is YeXiu.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:04.02,0:00:06.85,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You can call me Mr.Ye
Dialogue: 1,0:00:06.85,0:00:09.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Welcome to my English class!
Dialogue: 1,0:00:09.52,0:00:13.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We'll speak English in my class.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.00,0:00:15.07,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}English is my first language,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:15.07,0:00:21.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}so whatever your English level is, I can teach you!
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.20,0:00:25.42,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If you've never learnt English before,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.42,0:00:28.65,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}and have trouble understanding me, no worries,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.65,0:00:30.70,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I can speak Chinese with you.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.70,0:00:33.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Although I've only been learning Chinese for a year,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.30,0:00:38.47,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}so my hope is that we can speak English to each other.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.47,0:00:45.37,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)\fscx88}I think the best way to learn a language is to learn about the culture that the language comes from.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:45.37,0:00:51.55,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}so, in my class, you can learn about North American culture.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.55,0:00:55.07,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If you already have an English textbook to learn from,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.07,0:00:59.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I can help you understand your course's material.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.40,0:01:02.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now, let's learn English together!
